| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3047 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4c7e0ade-920f-5fc2-a837-bb5c4d272a22"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
